preference.name: PSE_default_view_type
preference.preference_description: Determines which view type preference Design Context and Structure Manager queries use. By default, the system uses the TC_NX_View_Type preference, which in turn, is set to view by default. Valid Values: A single string as a value; the string must be a valid Teamcenter preference, set to a valid query type.
